quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  33,16,keh do ke agar tum marnay ya maaray se bhagtay ho to bhagna tum ko faida nahi day ga aur is waqt tum bohat hi kam faida uthao ge
  33,17,keh do ke agar khuda tumahray sath buraiee ka iradah kere to kon tum ko is se bacha sakta hai ya agar tum par meharbani karni chahay to ( kon is ko hata sakta hai ) aur yeh log khuda ke siwa kisi ko nah apna dost payen ge aur nah madadgaar
  33,18,khuda tum mein se un logon ko bhi jaanta hai jo ( logon ko ) mana karte hain aur apne bhaiyon se kehte hain ke hamaray paas chalay aao. aur larai mein nahi atay magar kam
  33,19,( yeh is liye ke ) tumahray baray mein bukhal karte hain. phir jab dar ( ka waqt ) aeye to tum un ko dekho ke tumhari taraf dekh rahay hain ( aur ) unn ki ankhen ( isi terhan ) phir rahi hain jaisay kisi ko mout se ghashi aa rahi ho. phir jab khauf jata rahay to taiz zabanon ke sath tumahray baray mein zabaan Darazi karen aur maal mein bukhal karen. yeh log ( haqeeqat mein ) imaan laaye hi nah they to khuda ne un ke aamaal barbaad kar diye. aur yeh khuda ko aasaan tha
  33,20,( khauf ke sabab ) khayaal karte hain ke faujein nahi gayeen. aur agar lashkar ajayeen to tamanna karen ke ( kash ) ganwaroon mein ja rahen ( aur ) tumhari khabar poocha karen. aur agar tumahray darmain hon to larai nah karen magar kam
  33,21,tum ko paighambar khuda ki pairwi ( karni ) behtar hai ( yani ) is shakhs ko jisay khuda ( se milnay ) aur roz qayamat ( ke anay ) ki umeed ho aur woh khuda ka zikar kasrat se karta ho
  33,22,aur jab mominoun ne ( kafiroon ke ) lashkar ko dekha to kehnay lagey yeh wohi hai jis ka khuda aur is ke paighambar ne hum se wadakiya tha aur khuda aur is ke paighambar ne sach kaha tha. aur is se un ka imaan aur itaat aur ziyada hogayi
